(see Pešić 
<emphasis box="[955,1006,552,577]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">et al</emphasis>
. 
<number box="[1021,1084,552,578]" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" value="2005.0">2005</number>
a). Thus 
<taxonomicName box="[1183,1314,552,577]" class="Arachnida" family="Sperchonidae" genus="Sperchon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="beneckei">
<emphasis box="[1183,1314,552,577]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">S. beneckei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be considered a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[529,687,589,614]" class="Arachnida" family="Sperchonidae" genus="Sperchon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="2" pageNumber="45" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="algeriensis">
<emphasis box="[529,687,589,614]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="45">S. algeriensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
